\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces The full project flow in one line: raw data is cleaned, the model learns patterns, results are measured, and the final system is served through an API.}}{1}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
