\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {23}{\ignorespaces Complete two-stage data refinery pipeline: Stage 1 (Notebooks 01) transforms raw files into clean numeric data; Stage 2 (Notebook 03) partitions for training and evaluation, producing the production training set.}}{10}{figure.caption.28}\protected@file@percent }
